= Installation

From the root directory of this application type:

  rake install
  
This will launch the install wizard, which will take you step by step in setting up RAM.

If you have problems installing RAM, consult the support section of our 
website, which can be found here: http://www.locusfoc.us/ram/pages/docs.

Additionally, you can come by our IRC channel at:

  Server  : irc.freenode.net
  Channel : #ram

We hope you enjoy RAM!


